      | Name                         | TestDate            |
      | Is this field required       | No                  |
      | Is this field locked         | No                  |
      | Should the data be unique    | No                  |
      | Who is this field visible to | Not visible         |
    And I press "Save changes"

    Given I set the following fields to these values:
